  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK936">
<l>akaṭārā ralla luḻapparcū teṉṉum</l>
<l> mukaṭiyāṉ mūṭappaṭ ṭār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are swallowed by the goddess called "gambling" will never have their hunger satisfied, but suffer the pangs of hell in the next world.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
